Secure Trust Bank Appoints Sergeant to Board, Sunday Times Says

-- B y   P a t r i c i a   K u o
-- 
2011-10-23T11:25:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/secure-trust-bank-appoints-sergeant-to-board-sunday-times-says.html
Secure Trust Bank Plc appointed
Carol Sergeant as a non-executive director ahead of its planned
listing on the London Stock Exchange, the Sunday Times reported,
without saying where it obtained the information.  Sergeant left Lloyds Banking Group Plc as chief risk
officer in January.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Patricia Kuo in London at 
